parameters: \nc<Slaver Guard>Halt! You're not supposed to be in here!
\nc<Emily>If you put down your weapons, I'll let you go.
If not then you'll end up like the other guards.
\nc<Slaver Guard>Lanius, should we take them alive?
that would gladly buy ones as young as them. \!That's
a little disgusting but money is money!
\nc<Lanius>You got guts kid. Let's just see how much
of a fight you really can endure!
\nc<Emily>Let's make sure we finish off all of the guards
before we free the slaves here.
\nc<Nika>That's still the plan. Then we free your friend
Daric then we liberate the slaves.
